WHY DUAL LICENSING?

CC BY-SA ensures that anyone who downloads and redistributes
the full database keeps it open (like Wikipedia).

CC BY (no SA) for API responses means developers can build
proprietary apps on top of our API without being forced to
open-source their entire application. This encourages
ecosystem growth while still requiring attribution.

